<div id="sdfootnote20">
<p><a class="sdfootnotesym" href="#sdfootnote20anc" name="sdfootnote20sym">20</a><span style="color: #000080"><span lang="zxx"><span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #666666"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: xx-small"><b>APNZ (2013). </b></span></span></span></span></span></span><em><span style="color: #666666"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: xx-small"><i><b>Welfare Reforms Affecting Children &#8211; CPAG</b></i></span></span></span></em><span style="color: #000080"><span lang="zxx"><span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #666666"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: xx-small"><b>. [ONLINE] Available at: http://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&amp;objectid=11144248. [Last Accessed 17/05/2014].</b></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</div>
<div id="sdfootnote21">
<p class="sdfootnote"><a class="sdfootnotesym" href="#sdfootnote21anc" name="sdfootnote21sym">21</a><span style="color: #666666"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: xx-small"><b>Lindsay Mitchell (2011). </b></span></span></span><em><span style="color: #666666"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: xx-small"><i><b>Child poverty &#8211; what is left unsaid</b></i></span></span></span></em><span style="color: #666666"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: xx-small"><b>. [ONLINE] Available at: http://welfarereform.co.nz/MR2011SEP22.html. [Last Accessed 17/05/2014].</b></span></span></span></p>
