<div id="post-content-1104" class="post-1104 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-community category-elections category-governance category-news full">
	
	<h1 class="entry-title full-title"><a href="http://onewaiheke.org/2014/05/how-you-can-stop-the-spread-of-misinformation/" title="Permanent link to How you can stop the spread of misinformation" rel="bookmark" rev="post-1104">How you can stop the spread of misinformation</a></h1>
	
	<div class="entry-content full-content">
<p>On Waiheke there are a few people that are currently spreading misinformation online about the current local board.</p>
<p>The main outlets for this misinformation is a blog and Facebook.</p>
<p>Here are some practical steps you can take to help reduce the spread of that misinformation.</p>
<p><a href="http://onewaiheke.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/You-can-help-stop-the-spread-of-misinformation.png"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1105" alt="You-can-help-stop-the-spread-of-misinformation" src="http://onewaiheke.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/You-can-help-stop-the-spread-of-misinformation.png" width="510" height="287" /></a></p>
<div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"><div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-icon-text sd-sharing"><h3 class="sd-title">Share this:</h3><div class="sd-content"><ul><li class="share-email"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-email sd-button share-icon" href="http://onewaiheke.org/2014/05/how-you-can-stop-the-spread-of-misinformation/?share=email" title="Click to email this to a friend"><span>Email</span></a></li><li class="share-twitter"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-twitter sd-button share-icon" href="http://onewaiheke.org/2014/05/how-you-can-stop-the-spread-of-misinformation/?share=twitter" title="Click to share on Twitter" id="sharing-twitter-1104"><span>Twitter</span></a></li><li class="share-google-plus-1"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-google-plus-1 sd-button share-icon" href="http://onewaiheke.org/2014/05/how-you-can-stop-the-spread-of-misinformation/?share=google-plus-1" title="Click to share on Google+" id="sharing-google-1104"><span>Google</span></a></li><li class="share-print"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-print sd-button share-icon" href="http://onewaiheke.org/2014/05/how-you-can-stop-the-spread-of-misinformation/" title="Click to print"><span>Print</span></a></li><li><a href="#" class="sharing-anchor sd-button share-more"><span>More</span></a></li><li class="share-end"></li></ul><div class="sharing-hidden"><div class="inner" style="display: none;"><ul><li class="share-digg"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-digg sd-button share-icon" href="http://onewaiheke.org/2014/05/how-you-can-stop-the-spread-of-misinformation/?share=digg" title="Click to Digg this post"><span>Digg</span></a></li><li class="share-facebook"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-facebook sd-button share-icon" href="http://onewaiheke.org/2014/05/how-you-can-stop-the-spread-of-misinformation/?share=facebook" title="Share on Facebook" id="sharing-facebook-1104"><span>Facebook</span></a></li><li class="share-end"></li><li class="share-reddit"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-reddi